ing: 1 (8 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
des: "This is a creamy, luscious, coffee-flavored dip for fruit -- strawberries, tart apples, pineapple, grapes, etc. It's perfect for bridal or baby showers, and it's quick and easy to make."
ins: Place cream cheese, sour cream, brown sugar and coffee-flavored liqueur in a medium bowl. Blend together with an electric mixer until smooth. Fold in thawed frozen whipped topping. Chill in the refrigerator until serving.
